  "texts": [
    "Firstly, nuclear power and AI have different characteristics and risks, limiting the direct application of the IAEA's case in all aspects.",
    "Secondly, international agreement and standardization can be time-consuming and may not reflect the situations and needs of all countries.",
    "Thirdly, conflicts or redundancy with existing regulatory systems may occur.",
    "This paper proposes alternative approaches to address these limitations and problems.",
    "Firstly, considering the characteristics and risks of AI, the establishment of an independent regulatory system can be considered."
  ]
